<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB05136</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT ESTABLISHING A SYSTEM OF ACCREDITATION FOR GARBAGE COLLECTION SERVICE BUSINESS, PROVIDING FUNDS THEREFOR AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Seeks to mandate the Environmental Management Bureau to establish and operationalize a system of accreditation for owners, contractors, and/or operators of garbage collection or hauling service businesses for a more systematized and efficient implementation of RA9003 - the Ecological Solid Waste Management Act of 2000.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BATOCABE, RODEL M., GARBIN, ALFREDO JR. A., CO, CHRISTOPHER S.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2017-02-27</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Sy-Alvarado (080 2017-03-08)</td><td>2. Tambunting (000 2018-01-23)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRADE AND INDUSTRY ON 2017-03-06</td></tr></table>